[Install]

  - Unzip the IPAM software under any path.
  - Run "IPAM.install", and if you change the path of IPAM software, please run "IPAM.install" again.
  - Set the environment variables, add PATH or add alias. For example alias IPAM='path/IPAM'.
  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

[USAGE]

  >>> IPAM --file [path] --pathway [path].
  IPAM --file path/data_folder --pathway path/pathway_folder
  IPAM --file data_folder --pathway pathway_folder
  
--file - The first parameter of IPAM.
  - The path of the input data, all files in the folder will be read automatically, both absolute and relative path are allowed.
  
--pathway - The second parameter of IPAM.
  - The path of the pathway input, all files in pathway will be calculated in this analysis, each pathway contains the gene symbol list in the pathway.
  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

[EXAMPLE]

  ./IPAM --file ${pw_work}/IPAM.files/IPAM.test --pathway ${pw_work}/IPAM.files/IPAM.KEGG"
  
  NOTE:the KEGG pathways data were download from KEGG database in May, 2019, which contains 318 KEGG pathways.


